The paper deals with object detection using deep convolutional neural networks, which is a common topic in computer vision (cs.CV). The paper also proposes a novel method for weakly supervised learning, which falls under the category of machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The use of web images and the construction of a web dataset also involves information retrieval (cs.IR) and multimedia (cs.MM) aspects.
